OL,5, The wife of Hairy Bikers star Dave     
OL,6, Myers has posted a touching tribute to 
OL,7, her "wonderful, brave man" following   
OL,8, his death from cancer at the age of 66.
OL,10,FMyers was known as one half of the     
OL,11,Fmuch-loved TV cooking duo.             
OL,13,F"Rest in peace, my love," Liliana Myers
OL,14,Fwrote on Facebook. "My wonderful, brave
OL,15,Fman! Till next time we meet!"          
OL,17,FOther tributes have flooded in from    
OL,18,Fthose who worked with him and his TV   
OL,19,Fpartner Si King, and met them during   
OL,20,Ftheir motorcycle trips around the UK.  
